graphs.text: #   This page is the innermost verso panel of a six-panel fold-out.
#   Two blocks of text and and two rows of plants:
#      [2,1]..[2,3] between pagas 1 and 2; roots and leaves.
#   There are also two containers (unlabeled?) crammed into the left
#   margin; they look as if they were added as an afterthought.
#   "Fair copies" of some of these drawings are found elsewhere:
# labels on first row of plants
# plant [1,1] - dark leaf, roots, light stem
# plant [1,3] - round starbust flower?, arrowhead leaves
# hairy two-story bulb with bunch of mousetail roots at bottom
# plant [1,4] - half-potato vertically striped root, lobate leaves
# with bunch of mousetail roots at bottom
# plant [1,5] - long pinnate leaves, "bunch of fingers" root
# labels on second row of plants
# plant [2,1] - four-lobed truncated tuber with bunch of roots
# at the bottom; lanceolate leaves with serrated edges.
# plant [2,2] - squatting cone of mousetail roots, funnel-like root
# hub, large leaf with pointy fingers.
# plant [2,3] - round palmlike leaf, bunch of snakelike roots
